column3: I'm drawing out the Darkness. Get ready!
It worked, Gaia! We've done it!
So this all took place a hundred years ago...
But what does it have to do with Gaia?
I know this place...! It's the gaol in Eulmore!
She deserves...all the happiness...in the world...
One that we may share for all eternity.
I won't give up on our future, Gaia! No matter what!
